author: daniel
msg: We now set MAKEINFO to the path configure found for it
If 'makeinfo' is found, MAKEINFO is set to the full path. If it isn't found,
MAKEINFO is set to a verbose echo string, as that makes the 'doc-info' and
other make targets that use $(MAKEINFO) output the command line it can't run.
